<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>forgot user pass page</title>
  
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/homePagesCSS/forgotPassPage.css">

</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <div class="headerTitle">
      Welcome to <span>landbook.com</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pageHeading">
    User's forgot password page
  </div>


  <div class="aboutContainer">
    <div class="about1">
      This is the page by <span class="logo">Landbook</span> where customers can recover their landbook account by entering some details about them.
    </div>
    <div class="skipLink">
      <div class="link">
        <a href="/home/login">Back to login page</a> 
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about2">
      Customers can click <span class="skip">Back to login page</span> if they remembered their initial <span class="logo">Landbook</span> account password. Otherwise, Users have to enter their username, contact number given, email account to recover their account and make a new password with same initial information eg. same username, contact number, email account if they want or they can change any given information too.
    </div>
  </div>

  <% if(error.length > 0) { %>
    <div class="flash flash-error">
      <%= error %>
    </div>
  <% } %>
  <% if(success.length > 0) { %>
    <div class="flash flash-success">
      <%= success %>
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="loginBox">
    <div class="title">
      Enter correct details in order to Forgot password
    </div>
    <form action="/us/user/forgottingPass" method="post" onsubmit="return validatePassword()">
      <input type="userName" placeholder="Enter your username" class="username" name="username" required>
      <input type="number" placeholder="Your correct contact number" class="number" name="contactNumber" required>
      <input type="email" placeholder="abc@gmail.com" class="email" name="email" required>
      <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="login">
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footers">
      <a href="/home/aboutus" class="footerLinks">
        Contact us
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="footers">
      <a href="/home/aboutus" class="footerLinks">
        About us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>


  <script>
    function validatePassword() {
      const input = document.getElementById('password');
      const errorMsg = document.getElementById('errorMsg');
      if(input.value.length > 5) {
        errorMsg.textContent = 'Password must be at least 5 characters long.';
        return false;
      }
      return true;
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>